[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0087","title":"IBM AIX Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 Telnet 协议数据包，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致系统完全冻结，合法用户无法登录或访问服务器资源。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本，攻击门槛低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，IBM 已在后续维护版本中修复此问题。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并使用 refresh -s inetd 生效，改用 SSH 替代 telnet 服务，同时在防火墙上限制对 23/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0087","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0087","http://www.osvdb.org/7992"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0733","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0486","title":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 超链接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的超链接（hyperlink）消息，导致 AIM 客户端在处理该链接时崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需认证即可触发，影响所有使用 AIM 3.5 版本的用户。由于 AIM 客户端未能正确验证超链接输入，攻击者构造的畸形链接可触发程序异常，导致服务不可用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0486"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-01","updated":"1998-02-01","remediation":"建议立即卸载 AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 客户端，该产品已于 2017 年 12 月 15 日停止服务，官方不再提供安全更新。在浏览器设置中移除 AIM 协议处理程序（aim://）的自动关联，防止恶意超链接自动触发客户端。作为替代方案，迁移至支持端到端加密的现代即时通讯软件（如 Signal、Telegram）。如因历史原因必须使用，建议在防火墙或网络代理层面拦截 aim:// 协议流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0491","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0296","title":"Solaris volrmmount 程序任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统的 volrmmount 程序存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可以读取系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，需要本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0296"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1998-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Oracle Sun Security Bulletin 162 提供的补丁程序，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本。对于已停止支持的 Solaris 版本，建议迁移到受支持的 Solaris 11 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T16:49:07.408471690+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/162","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0296"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0448","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0264","title":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 中的 CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制的 URL 路径参数，绕过路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件（如密码文件、配置文件等）。该漏洞影响 htmlscript 2.x 版本，攻击者只需发送 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级中等，建议升级至最新版本或禁用该 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0264"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.847","remediation":"升级 Miva htmlscript 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题；如产品已停止维护，应立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中移除 htmlscript CGI 程序。临时缓解措施：在 Apache/Nginx 层面配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 的 URL 请求，或通过 .htaccess 限制对 htmlscript 脚本的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0264","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20434","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.829","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2d13d37d-5c85-422a-bd4e-7e51f93842cc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0271","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0125","title":"SGI IRIX mailx 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 mailx 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序对用户输入的数据长度缺乏充分校验，当攻击者向 mailx 程序传入特制的超长参数时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致程序异常崩溃。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞实现权限提升，获取 root 权限。该漏洞同样影响 RedHat Linux 4.2 和 Solaris 2.6 系统。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0125"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.563","remediation":"SGI IRIX 用户请安装 SGI 安全公告 19980605-01-PX 提供的 mailx 补丁；RedHat Linux 4.2 用户升级 mailx 到已修复版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装 Sun 官方 mailx 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 mailx 的 setuid 位：chmod u-s /bin/mailx。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19312","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0125","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0125.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0049","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0049.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0013","title":"OpenSSH ssh-agent 凭据窃取漏洞","description":"SSH 协议中的 ssh-agent 程序存在凭证泄露漏洞，本地攻击者可通过访问 ssh-agent 进程获取已存储的 SSH 私钥及认证凭证，从而伪装成目标用户登录远程系统。该漏洞影响广泛使用 ssh-agent 的各类 SSH 实现环境，攻击者需要已获得目标系统的本地访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0013"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.890","remediation":"升级至支持 SSH2 协议的 OpenSSH_3.0+ 版本并禁用 SSH1 协议（在 sshd_config 中设置 Protocol 2）；同时限制 ssh-agent 的 socket 文件权限（0700）并建议用户在非信任环境中避免使用 ssh-agent 转发功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0049.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0045","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0014","title":"多厂商 CDE dtappgather 未授权权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境中的 dtappgather 程序存在文件权限更改漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该程序获取非授权提权访问权限或导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20/11.0、IBM AIX 4.3、SCO Unixware 7.0 及 Sun Solaris 2.6 等操作系统，攻击者通过向 dtappgather 发送特制请求即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0014"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.147","remediation":"联系各操作系统厂商获取对应补丁：HP-UX 安装 PHSS_15068 补丁包，AIX 安装 IY66454 更新，移除 dtappgather 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtappgather），或在无需 CDE 环境时卸载 dtlogin/CDE 套件以彻底消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/185","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9801-075","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19108","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0014","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-