57","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0271","title":"Progressive Networks Real Video Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Progressive Networks Real Video server（pnserver）存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制数据包触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃，影响正常视频流服务。该漏洞利用难度较低，攻击条件简单，但仅影响服务可用性，不会导致数据泄露或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0271"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.730","remediation":"建议立即升级至已修复该漏洞的 Progressive Networks RealVideo Server 最新版本，或从网络层面在防火墙上限制对 pnserver 服务端口（默认 TCP 7070）的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。由于该产品已长期停止维护，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的流媒体服务器（如 Wowza Streaming Engine 或 Nginx-RTMP）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0271.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/pnserver.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82096/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0271.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1241","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0958","title":"Todd Miller sudo 1.5.x 本地权限提升代码执行漏洞","description":"sudo 1.5.x 版本存在路径遍历导致的本地代码执行漏洞。由于 sudo 在处理命令路径时未能正确过滤“..（点点）”目录遍历序列，本地已通过认证的低权限用户可在调用 sudo 执行命令时构造包含“..”的恶意路径，绕过预期的命令限制，使 sudo 以 root 权限执行攻击者指定的任意命令。该漏洞影响 sudo 1.5.x 系列版本，攻击前提是攻击者需具备本地登录权限且被授权使用 sudo。利用方式简单，只需在 sudo 命令参数中插入“..”目录穿越路径即可提升权限执行任意命令，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0958"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:24.480","remediation":"升级 sudo 至 1.5.9 或更高版本（如 Debian 提供的修复包），以修复路径遍历导致的本地命令执行问题。若无法立即升级，可临时收紧 sudoers 配置、移除存在风险的命令授权，并限制普通用户对 sudo 二进制文件及配置目录的写权限作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88465708614896&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0958.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0958.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0958","https://github.com/trifectatechfoundation/sudo-rs/blob/e5a01fd7a20a5bfe5da6bc1b5cf7628e721c35c8/docs/sudo-cve.md","https://github.com/TH3xACE/SUDO_KILLER/blob/27ccd0e2d39528f9383864d5e3fe87f7bd2f60d3/CVE/cve.sudover.vuln.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0958.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0958.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4vxh-pf2c-r9qp/GHSA-4vxh-pf2c-r9qp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0958.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88416/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1376","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1376.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1176","title":"cidentd identd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"cidentd 软件中的 ident 守护进程存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者通过在 .authlie 配置脚本中写入超长字符串，可触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够覆盖内存数据并执行任意代码，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞攻击前提为拥有本地访问权限，利用难度较低，可造成权限提升，对系统机密性、完整性和可用性构成严重影响（CVSS 评分 7.2）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1176"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.877","remediation":"建议立即升级 cidentd 至 1.3.2 及以上修复版本，该版本已修复 .authlie 文件读取时的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无需 ident 认证服务，应直接卸载 cidentd 或禁用该守护进程；需继续使用时，限制仅可信任用户访问系统，并通过防火墙过滤 113 端口入站请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88466930416716&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90554230925545&w=2","http://spisa.act.uji.es/spi/progs/codigo/www.hack.co.za/exploits/daemon/ident/cidentd.c","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1176.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1176","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1176.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1176.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fvwm-29jh-q698/GHSA-fvwm-29jh-q698.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83045/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1176.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000251.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--409b1a93-46ca-4c5a-8775-db10781d0caa.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1376.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0203","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0086","title":"IBM AIX routed 远程敏感文件修改漏洞","description":"AIX 系统中的 routed 路由守护进程存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RIP 路由协议报文，利用该漏洞可修改系统敏感文件，从而获得非授权访问权限或造成系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 AIX 操作系统的 routed 服务，攻击者可通过伪造路由更新实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0086"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.940","remediation":"升级 AIX 至受支持的最新版本（7.2 TL5/7.3 及以上），该版本已不再使用存在漏洞的 routed 实现。若无法升级，立即停止 routed 服务（`stopsrc -s routed`）并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释相关行，同时在防火墙侧阻断外部对 UDP 520 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0767","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0513","title":"Linux Kernel ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 版本中存在 ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者通过向目标网络的广播地址发送源地址伪造的 ICMP Echo 请求数据包，该网络中的所有主机都会向伪造的源地址（受害者）发送 ICMP Echo 响应，形成流量放大攻击，导致目标系统网络带宽被耗尽而无法提供正常服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 及 Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、Solaris 等多个操作系统版本，攻击条件为目标网络允许定向广播（Directed Broadcast）且未配置相关防护措施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0513"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.307","remediation":"在路由器上禁用 IP 定向广播功能（no ip directed-broadcast），并在各主机操作系统层面禁止响应 ICMP 广播请求（如 Linux 设置 net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1），同时部署网络入口过滤防止源地址伪造。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0513","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19117","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fec368cf82886628cf7251fa55925507d7e50c60/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0513","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0513.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q2cm-72c7-798h/GHSA-q2cm-72c7-798h.json","https://github.com/nbrito/source/blob/7cf72f44a54cbe709dbbac0935c73bf4ba0649d0/c/t50/README.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_800_900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000249.txt","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0560","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0341","title":"Debian Linux deliver 邮件程序本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 系统中的 mail 程序 \"deliver\" 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限，危害等级高，影响 Debian Linux 系统。建议及时安装厂商发布的安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0341"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.357","remediation":"升级 Linux 发行版至至少 Debian 3.0（Woody）以上版本，该版本已移除有漏洞的 deliver 程序，改用更安全的邮件传输代理。如因特殊原因仍使用 deliver，立即将其 SUID 权限移除（chmod u-s /usr/bin/deliver），并迁移至 exim 或 postfix 等现代 MTA。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0547","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0547.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0331","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0/4.0.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可构造特制网页或 URL，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器崩溃或执行任意代码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上 IE 4.0 及 4.0.1 版本，攻击复杂度低且无需认证，仅需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0331"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.197","remediation":"立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本，Microsoft 已在 IE 5.0 中修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用的旧系统，应停止使用 IE 4.0 并迁移至 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等受支持的现代浏览器。如无法升级浏览器，可通过防火墙限制受感染主机对外部恶意服务器的 80/443 端口访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/